title: my lol launcher is not launching the game
body:
my lol launcher is not launching to the login page
the symbol "league of legends" is projected and the process continues but there is no lauching
i have tried all the ways the lol support page discussed and yet nothing is changing
i tried reinstalling lol but it ends up in same error. thus i want a solution on how to make my lol work

replies.body: Getting stuck at the logo may indicate a security setting that's failing to launch.  Run through the [permissions](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions) guide to make sure you're being allowed to load the client.  Let me know if you have any questions!
